<p>Brent Councilâ€™s <a href="/images/st-raphaels-faq.pdf">infopack</a> (distributed to residents in Dec 2019 ahead of the ballot) makes it clear that if infill is the preferred option then their estate may also not receive any investment for improving current housing conditions:</p>

<p><img src="/images/st-raphaels-faq.png" alt="" />
